High-Level Document (HLD)


Project Title: To-Do List Application
Overview : 
The To-Do List Application is a simple, web-based application that allows users to add and delete tasks. The application provides an intuitive user interface for managing daily tasks.

Key Features : 

Add tasks to a to-do list
Delete tasks from the to-do list
Persistent state within a session

Technology Stack : 

Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
Libraries: None
Backend: None
Database: None

User Interface:

The user interface consists of a main container with a task input field and a list of tasks. Each task can be checked off or deleted.
